WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:23.880 --> 01:25.640
What... What AIDS?

01:25.640 --> 01:26.240
Who told you that?

01:26.240 --> 01:27.520
Nonsense! These are simply rumors!

01:27.800 --> 01:28.800
If it's nonsense,

01:28.800 --> 01:29.840
why didn't you argue with them?

01:31.039 --> 01:32.240
How?

01:33.039 --> 01:33.880
How am I even able

01:33.880 --> 01:35.360
to argue with so many people?

01:35.360 --> 01:36.479
You are so ignorant.

01:36.479 --> 01:37.880
Words can kill, you know?

01:38.039 --> 01:38.759
But if we don't make it clear,

01:38.759 --> 01:40.280
we keep getting bullied
and dragged into trouble,

01:40.320 --> 01:41.520
no matter where we go.

01:41.520 --> 01:42.880
Who bullied you?

01:42.880 --> 01:44.080
We've already moved to a new place.

01:44.080 --> 01:45.039
She's dead.

01:45.080 --> 01:46.160
Everything is in the past.

01:46.160 --> 01:46.960
No, it's not.

01:47.960 --> 01:48.920
What do you want, then?

01:49.479 --> 01:50.360
An explanation.

01:50.680 --> 01:52.840
It's the only way to shut them up.

01:53.080 --> 01:54.880
Hiding and running away

01:54.880 --> 01:56.240
will only make things worse.

01:56.280 --> 01:58.039
What do you hope to explain?

01:58.720 --> 01:59.880
Don't act superior

01:59.880 --> 02:01.560
just because you've been to school.

02:02.680 --> 02:04.040
This is about your education.

02:04.040 --> 02:05.080
Don't squabble with me.

02:05.240 --> 02:06.840
Focus on your studies instead.

02:07.360 --> 02:08.680
Give me a break, will you?

02:08.680 --> 02:10.199
Let me have some peace.

02:17.440 --> 02:18.280
Didn't we agree

02:18.280 --> 02:20.720
to not talk about the past
after moving here?

02:21.680 --> 02:23.840
The past is weighing heavily on her.

02:24.079 --> 02:25.640
She is a big girl now.

02:25.640 --> 02:26.920
Try a different approach

02:26.920 --> 02:28.800
when you talk to her.

02:29.079 --> 02:30.240
This conversation is over.

02:36.920 --> 02:37.920
A shot for me, then.

02:40.900 --> 02:45.829
[Episode 2]
[The Blade of Gossip]

02:57.280 --> 02:58.680
Nice handwriting,

02:59.440 --> 03:00.440
almost identical to mine.

03:03.280 --> 03:03.960
This is the first

03:03.960 --> 03:05.640
and the last time
I'm doing your homework.

03:06.760 --> 03:08.480
People would do anything to do this.

03:08.480 --> 03:09.840
But their handwriting is awful.

03:09.840 --> 03:10.960
I'm not obliged to help you.

03:10.960 --> 03:11.320
Hey.

03:11.760 --> 03:12.600
It's not an obligation.

03:13.480 --> 03:14.400
This is compensation.

03:31.760 --> 03:34.160
Were you talking to Ming Sheng just now?

03:37.120 --> 03:38.840
Did you know him before?

03:39.640 --> 03:41.560
I heard him calling you
"Beiyu's little sister".

03:42.360 --> 03:43.600
Do you have an older sister?

03:44.640 --> 03:46.440
No, I am the oldest.

03:46.440 --> 03:47.440
I have a younger brother.

03:51.600 --> 03:53.360
Are you two close?

03:54.360 --> 03:55.440
I just want you

03:55.680 --> 03:56.440
to stay cautious.

03:56.800 --> 03:57.560
Why?

03:58.320 --> 04:00.520
Watch out for the girls in our class.

04:00.880 --> 04:02.040
Ming Sheng is quite something.

04:02.440 --> 04:04.120
Every student in Huanzhou

04:04.120 --> 04:05.640
knows about him.

04:06.480 --> 04:08.040
He's good-looking, loyal to friends,

04:08.040 --> 04:09.640
and truly one of a kind.

04:10.280 --> 04:10.880
Sheng.

04:11.960 --> 04:13.440
Let's hang out after school.

04:14.000 --> 04:14.720
Sure.

04:14.720 --> 04:15.120
Great.

04:15.120 --> 04:16.600
Get the guys from Class 4 too.

04:17.000 --> 04:18.079
I can't make it today.

04:18.160 --> 04:18.959
I have training.

04:19.360 --> 04:21.480
My homework has been settled.

04:23.080 --> 04:24.400
I'll wake up early tomorrow
to finish mine.

04:24.400 --> 04:25.160
I've settled mine.

04:26.240 --> 04:28.440
He is rash, mischievous, and arrogant,

04:28.440 --> 04:29.840
more like one of the worst.

04:31.680 --> 04:34.240
Ming Sheng takes a lot of leave
and submits his homework late.

04:34.280 --> 04:36.440
But it's only because
he is exceptionally talented.

04:36.440 --> 04:37.600
He won

04:37.600 --> 04:40.840
first prize
in the national biology competition.

04:41.080 --> 04:42.120
He may be mischievous,

04:42.120 --> 04:44.080
but he still gets good grades.

04:45.080 --> 04:46.880
He accomplished great things

04:46.880 --> 04:48.680
without being a bookworm.

04:48.680 --> 04:50.760
Of course he'd be popular in school.

05:29.560 --> 05:30.360
Let's go.

05:30.360 --> 05:31.720
Bye.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.200
They are playing basketball.

05:34.360 --> 05:35.640
Come, watch the game with me.

05:38.000 --> 05:39.520
I don't get it.

05:39.520 --> 05:41.560
We were trying to help out that day.

05:51.880 --> 05:53.080
The diner owner

05:53.080 --> 05:54.560
insisted Sheng broke her chair.

05:54.560 --> 05:55.800
She filed a complaint to the school.

05:56.200 --> 05:58.320
You could explain it to Sun.

05:58.320 --> 05:59.240
There's no need for that.

05:59.720 --> 06:00.680
Are you sure?

06:01.600 --> 06:02.320
Stop right there!

06:07.830 --> 06:13.450
♪I used to think
that everything would turn out okay♪

06:15.250 --> 06:21.480
♪Making plans. Work hard.
You might succeed♪

06:21.880 --> 06:26.500
♪When you try, when you fail,
nothing is really easy♪

06:27.200 --> 06:29.580
♪That denying force♪

06:29.930 --> 06:34.350
♪Always feels like it's there,
where we least expect it♪

06:34.980 --> 06:37.350
♪Now you've wound up low♪

06:38.880 --> 06:39.840
Get out of my way!

06:39.840 --> 06:43.230
♪There is a feeling I can't let go♪

06:43.520 --> 06:44.640
What are you doing?

06:45.200 --> 06:47.830
♪Can't let go♪

06:48.560 --> 06:49.360
Where is the wallet?

06:50.960 --> 06:52.360
What are you talking about?

06:52.360 --> 06:57.920
♪You must stay in the lead and in control♪

06:57.920 --> 06:58.720
Where's the money?

06:59.520 --> 07:00.320
What are they doing?

07:00.320 --> 07:02.450
♪When you try, when you fail,
nothing is really easy♪

07:02.920 --> 07:03.720
Where's the money?

07:04.200 --> 07:05.000
In my pocket.

07:05.000 --> 07:06.840
♪That denying force♪

07:06.840 --> 07:08.960
Madam, the police have arrested
the pickpocket.

07:09.520 --> 07:10.560
My money is all here.

07:10.600 --> 07:11.920
Thank you so much, boys.

07:11.920 --> 07:13.040
I didn't lose a coin.

07:13.560 --> 07:15.040
Keep your wallet safe.

07:15.200 --> 07:16.240
I am Ye Zilin.

07:16.760 --> 07:18.000
I'll never forget that name.

07:19.640 --> 07:21.280
Madam, we are from Class 5, Grade 2.

07:22.080 --> 07:23.840
These are good boys.

07:25.560 --> 07:27.480
Ming Sheng is so charming.

07:27.920 --> 07:28.720
Another one.

07:28.720 --> 07:32.450
♪There is a feeling I can't let go♪

07:34.250 --> 07:36.250
♪Can't let go♪

07:41.560 --> 07:42.360
Qingyu?

07:43.159 --> 07:43.960
Are you all right?

07:45.360 --> 07:46.760
I wonder if Heaven

07:47.440 --> 07:48.480
sent Qiao Qingyu here

07:48.480 --> 07:50.080
to be our jester.

07:51.040 --> 07:53.560
Her clumsiness
is surprisingly refreshing.

07:54.520 --> 07:55.480
It's swelling.

08:02.800 --> 08:03.600
Qiao Qingyu.

08:08.760 --> 08:09.560
Are you all right?

08:10.160 --> 08:10.960
Mind your own business.

08:11.600 --> 08:12.600
Come on.

08:13.320 --> 08:14.560
You can't do my homework

08:14.560 --> 08:15.840
if you get brain damage from that.

08:17.240 --> 08:17.840
Hold this.

08:19.080 --> 08:20.040
Do as I say.

08:22.040 --> 08:23.040
I'm counting on you,

08:23.320 --> 08:24.280
Qiao Qingyu.

08:26.800 --> 08:28.240
I need your phone number.

08:29.240 --> 08:30.560
Don't get the wrong idea.

08:31.120 --> 08:33.000
I need it to talk to you
about my homework.

08:33.280 --> 08:34.679
You'd better reply promptly.

08:35.039 --> 08:36.240
I don't want any delays.

08:37.280 --> 08:38.360
I don't have a phone.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.280
For real?

08:42.720 --> 08:43.520
I have an idea.

08:43.880 --> 08:45.200
Give me your QQ contact.

08:50.480 --> 08:52.240
It's 38250127.

08:54.180 --> 08:55.930
[Huanzhou High School]

08:57.560 --> 08:58.560
Don't forget my homework.

08:59.880 --> 09:00.680
Qingyu!

09:06.480 --> 09:07.280
Ming Sheng?

09:08.400 --> 09:10.240
Is that really Ming Sheng?

09:11.040 --> 09:13.160
Nicely done, Qingyu.

09:13.360 --> 09:14.680
You managed to befriend

09:14.880 --> 09:17.160
the famous Ming Sheng
of Huanzhou High School already.

09:17.320 --> 09:18.840
Did you know how popular he is?

09:19.400 --> 09:19.960
Ming Sheng

09:20.160 --> 09:21.240
has been the MVP

09:21.240 --> 09:23.360
of the Students' League
three years in a row.

09:23.920 --> 09:25.880
All the guys worship him.

09:26.320 --> 09:26.800
Whatever he is...

09:26.800 --> 09:27.880
Qiao Jinyu.

09:28.480 --> 09:30.440
Could you put more effort
into your studies instead?

09:30.560 --> 09:31.720
Don't make basketball your life.

09:34.000 --> 09:34.800
But I...

09:35.800 --> 09:38.440
I spend all my energy and strength
on playing basketball.

09:38.440 --> 09:39.840
That's why I got into a sports school.

09:43.680 --> 09:45.120
What happened to your head?

09:49.520 --> 09:51.200
Did Ming Sheng hit you?

09:51.960 --> 09:52.840
Seriously?

09:53.440 --> 09:54.440
He didn't hit me.

09:54.440 --> 09:55.920
However, it was personal.

09:56.040 --> 09:57.720
But you two have no grudges.

09:57.720 --> 09:58.880
Why would he come after you?

09:59.040 --> 10:00.240
Because of her.

10:00.640 --> 10:02.040
We've moved to Huanzhou,

10:02.040 --> 10:03.320
but she never stops pestering us.

10:06.200 --> 10:06.640
Who is she?

10:08.880 --> 10:10.160
Is it Qiao Beiyu?

10:15.080 --> 10:16.240
Qiao Beiyu

10:16.240 --> 10:18.480
used to be a big shot in Shunyun.

10:19.080 --> 10:20.360
Every time we went out,

10:21.080 --> 10:22.880
people assumed

10:22.880 --> 10:24.800
we were her younger siblings.

10:25.320 --> 10:26.680
She was the center of attention,

10:27.240 --> 10:28.520
and we followed in her shadow,

10:29.120 --> 10:31.720
only able to shine
because of her presence.

10:32.120 --> 10:33.400
Good look is no good

10:33.400 --> 10:34.840
when it gets you into trouble.

10:37.680 --> 10:40.520
Sometimes I think

10:40.840 --> 10:42.720
you are jealous of her.

10:44.000 --> 10:45.240
I despise her.

10:55.240 --> 10:57.320
Your older sister is gorgeous
and has a great figure.

10:57.440 --> 10:58.480
I know the photos

10:58.480 --> 10:59.600
are going to be stunning.

11:06.400 --> 11:08.080
You can go home if you don't like this.

11:09.120 --> 11:10.920
I told you not to tag along.

11:11.640 --> 11:13.200
I didn't ask to come with you.

11:13.400 --> 11:15.360
Mom is worried about you
going out alone.

11:38.560 --> 11:39.480
Do you like it?

11:42.120 --> 11:44.000
Okay, you look like a superstar.

11:44.720 --> 11:45.520
Come on.

11:46.280 --> 11:48.000
Move the chin back a little.

11:48.080 --> 11:50.360
Raise your right hand slightly.

11:50.680 --> 11:52.520
Show me a wider smile.

11:53.160 --> 11:54.360
Yes. This is great!

11:55.400 --> 11:56.920
We'll take a few more shots.

12:00.450 --> 12:02.560
Little girl, did you take the earrings?

12:02.920 --> 12:03.680
What earrings?

12:04.080 --> 12:05.440
The ones in the jewelry case.

12:05.440 --> 12:06.880
You were trying them on.

12:06.880 --> 12:08.160
I can't find them.

12:08.360 --> 12:10.840
Could you help me look for them?

12:10.840 --> 12:11.720
I didn't take them.

12:12.360 --> 12:14.760
But there wasn't
anyone else in the shop.

12:16.480 --> 12:17.160
What's wrong?

12:17.160 --> 12:19.320
Beiyu, I didn't take the earrings.

12:19.320 --> 12:21.160
I only tried them on for a while

12:21.160 --> 12:22.760
and put them back.

12:23.160 --> 12:23.960
I...

12:24.160 --> 12:25.120
I didn't take them.

12:25.320 --> 12:26.760
Never mind.

12:26.760 --> 12:28.120
They're not that expensive.

12:28.400 --> 12:29.200
Qiao Qingyu.

12:29.600 --> 12:31.440
Put them back if you took them.

12:33.160 --> 12:34.520
I didn't!

12:35.520 --> 12:36.960
See for yourselves.

13:04.520 --> 13:05.320
My baby!

13:06.760 --> 13:07.560
Baby!

13:09.680 --> 13:10.640
I've been waiting.

13:10.640 --> 13:11.320
Give me a hug.

13:13.560 --> 13:14.480
I bought you flowers.

13:14.480 --> 13:15.840
Do you like them?

13:17.000 --> 13:17.720
Thanks.

13:17.720 --> 13:18.480
Don't mention it.

13:18.480 --> 13:20.560
You must be tired
of all those lessons today.

13:20.960 --> 13:22.200
It's all right.

13:22.200 --> 13:23.200
Let's go. I'm starving.

13:23.200 --> 13:25.080
Come, we are having seafood.

13:26.560 --> 13:27.360
Qiao Beiyu.

13:30.560 --> 13:32.000
I'm in Huanzhou for the IMO.

13:32.720 --> 13:34.640
Mom wants you to have the fruits.

13:36.880 --> 13:39.200
Who are you? I don't know you.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.880
You must be her sister back home.

13:44.280 --> 13:45.600
I said I don't know her.

13:45.600 --> 13:46.280
Let's go.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.480
I can see the resemblance.

13:53.640 --> 13:56.280
Qiao Beiyu! I don't know you either,
and I never will.

14:03.040 --> 14:03.960
Now that I think about it,

14:04.920 --> 14:06.280
I feel sorry for Beiyu sometimes.

14:07.160 --> 14:09.320
Growing up in Nanqiao Village,

14:09.560 --> 14:11.000
Mom and Dad barely
gave her any attention.

14:11.920 --> 14:14.400
And then, her life was cut short.

14:15.920 --> 14:16.920
She is dead.

14:16.920 --> 14:18.880
She can't hear them badmouthing her.

14:18.880 --> 14:19.720
But the rest of us?

14:19.720 --> 14:21.080
Why should we suffer because of her?

14:21.360 --> 14:22.840
We're the ones who deserve pity.

14:24.000 --> 14:25.440
She lived as a troublemaker.

14:25.520 --> 14:27.040
After she died,
she is still a burden to us all.

14:27.480 --> 14:28.360
Mom

14:28.360 --> 14:30.280
is scared of health textbooks.

14:30.760 --> 14:33.160
People mock me and pick on me
all the time.

14:34.280 --> 14:35.360
If I could,

14:35.600 --> 14:37.240
I wish I never had this sister.

15:50.840 --> 15:51.680
What now?

15:55.640 --> 15:56.360
Qiao Qingyu.

15:56.680 --> 15:57.200
Do you think

15:57.200 --> 15:58.520
I wouldn't make you pay?

15:58.720 --> 15:59.560
You spread false rumors.

15:59.920 --> 16:01.440
Qiao Beiyu died of appendicitis.

16:01.440 --> 16:02.680
It's not what you said.

16:03.560 --> 16:04.360
Can you prove it?

16:05.320 --> 16:06.520
Where is your proof, then?

16:06.520 --> 16:07.720
Don't slander her.

16:08.760 --> 16:09.760
I can prove it.

16:11.200 --> 16:12.520
Before your sister died,

16:12.600 --> 16:14.560
she was receiving treatments
in People's Hospital.

16:14.760 --> 16:15.840
The president of the hospital

16:16.600 --> 16:17.240
is my dad.

16:20.400 --> 16:22.800
Don't make claims
unless you can prove it.

16:46.800 --> 16:48.360
Let's get the training suits
from the dance studio.

16:48.360 --> 16:48.920
Okay.

16:56.320 --> 16:57.120
What are you looking at?

16:58.520 --> 16:59.880
See how different Mumu is

17:00.760 --> 17:01.840
from the girls in our class?

17:03.600 --> 17:04.359
Come on.

17:13.740 --> 17:14.900
I can prove it.

17:15.599 --> 17:16.800
Before your sister died,

17:17.000 --> 17:18.880
she was receiving treatments
in People's Hospital.

17:19.520 --> 17:22.000
The president of the hospital
is my dad.

17:23.240 --> 17:24.359
You guys carry on.

17:27.359 --> 17:28.240
Jiang Nian.

17:28.240 --> 17:30.400
Can I borrow your phone for a moment?

17:30.840 --> 17:31.520
Okay.

17:35.000 --> 17:37.680
[President of People's Hospital]

17:37.680 --> 17:41.480
[Ming Qiuxin, President
of the Huanzhou People's Hospital]

17:47.680 --> 17:48.640
It was appendicitis.

17:49.240 --> 17:50.720
I told you before.

17:52.920 --> 17:54.160
There were complications after surgery.

18:05.120 --> 18:05.760
Oh.

18:06.360 --> 18:07.160
You're back.

18:07.960 --> 18:09.000
Jinrui?

18:09.000 --> 18:10.280
You're back from school.

18:10.760 --> 18:12.520
Let me introduce.

18:12.520 --> 18:15.000
This is your future
cousin-in-law, Xiaoyun.

18:15.480 --> 18:16.920
Nice to meet you.
My name is Nie Xiaoyun.

18:17.440 --> 18:19.120
This is my cousin, Qiao Qingyu.

18:19.480 --> 18:20.800
Hello.

18:21.080 --> 18:22.560
Come, let's sit down.

18:22.560 --> 18:23.360
You too.

18:23.360 --> 18:24.240
Xiaoyun,

18:24.320 --> 18:25.120
has anyone told you

18:25.520 --> 18:27.280
you look like a movie star?

18:27.600 --> 18:28.760
Never.

18:29.240 --> 18:29.720
Fanghao.

18:31.400 --> 18:32.640
Could you slice some fruit for us?

18:33.360 --> 18:34.680
It's all right.

18:35.560 --> 18:36.760
Congratulations, Jinrui.

18:37.320 --> 18:37.960
Thank you.

18:37.960 --> 18:39.480
Impressive, Jinrui.

18:39.920 --> 18:41.880
She is so outstanding.

18:42.560 --> 18:43.240
I'm flattered.

18:44.760 --> 18:46.120
We've decided on the wedding date.

18:46.440 --> 18:47.720
Grandpa and Dad insisted

18:47.720 --> 18:49.600
that we drop by your house.

18:49.600 --> 18:51.640
We want to personally
invite you to our wedding.

18:51.920 --> 18:52.760
How thoughtful of you.

18:53.840 --> 18:55.520
When is the wedding reception?

18:56.520 --> 18:58.760
We plan to have it in Nanqiao Village

18:58.760 --> 19:00.000
next Chinese Lunar New Year.

19:00.880 --> 19:02.520
The folks of Nanqiao Village

19:02.520 --> 19:04.000
practically watched me grow up.

19:04.720 --> 19:05.320
I want

19:06.000 --> 19:07.840
to share the joy
of my wedding with them.

19:07.840 --> 19:09.800
You are the eldest child
in the whole family after all.

19:09.800 --> 19:12.720
Tradition dictates that you hold it
in your hometown.

19:13.400 --> 19:13.720
Yes.

19:13.720 --> 19:14.520
Jinrui,

19:14.560 --> 19:15.720
how did you manage

19:15.720 --> 19:17.640
to get such a beautiful wife?

19:18.400 --> 19:20.840
Jinrui, I heard you're
the department head now.

19:21.200 --> 19:22.120
I'm not the head.

19:22.360 --> 19:23.680
I just got promoted

19:23.840 --> 19:24.960
to Senior Staff Member.

19:25.920 --> 19:27.520
So, you're practically
a Section Chief then.

19:27.760 --> 19:29.080
Xiaoyun, did you know

19:29.360 --> 19:31.160
that Jinrui was
the first in Nanqiao Village

19:31.160 --> 19:33.560
to make it into one
of the Project 211 Universities?

19:33.800 --> 19:34.880
He is the first

19:34.880 --> 19:36.800
to become a Section Chief
in a state-owned corporation.

19:38.200 --> 19:40.160
My grandparents,

19:40.160 --> 19:42.040
Uncle Jiangsheng, and my father

19:42.160 --> 19:43.440
adored Jinrui more than anyone else.

19:43.440 --> 19:44.800
The rest of us were so jealous of him.

19:44.800 --> 19:46.640
Well, make Jinrui your role model.

19:46.640 --> 19:49.520
You may be cousins,
but you two are nothing alike.

19:52.320 --> 19:54.480
Xiaoyun, keep an eye on Jinrui.

19:54.560 --> 19:56.760
There is a long line of people

19:56.960 --> 19:59.400
waiting to marry their daughters to him.

20:00.360 --> 20:02.400
Watch your mouth.

20:02.520 --> 20:03.320
It's all right.

20:03.320 --> 20:05.040
I still see Qing and Yu

20:05.040 --> 20:05.800
as the kids

20:05.800 --> 20:07.360
who caught fish with me
in the village stream.

20:07.360 --> 20:09.240
We were all just kids back then.

20:09.560 --> 20:10.640
I rarely go back

20:10.640 --> 20:12.280
because I've been busy with work.

20:12.560 --> 20:13.960
I haven't seen Qing and Yu

20:13.960 --> 20:15.520
in a few years.

20:15.520 --> 20:16.880
Especially Yu.

20:17.040 --> 20:19.080
You've grown so tall now.

20:20.360 --> 20:21.080
Yeah.

20:21.080 --> 20:23.480
Jinrui and I went back
to Nanqiao Village last month.

20:23.480 --> 20:25.680
His mom showed us a lot of old photos.

20:26.360 --> 20:27.680
I also took some photos.

20:28.200 --> 20:29.000
Check this out.

20:32.800 --> 20:33.600
See this?

20:33.680 --> 20:35.720
The kid wearing the split trousers
is actually Yu.

20:35.960 --> 20:36.880
That is me?

20:37.560 --> 20:38.360
You looked hideous.

20:39.720 --> 20:42.120
Who is this? She is gorgeous.

20:47.120 --> 20:48.440
This is Qiao Beiyu.

20:50.680 --> 20:51.480
Beiyu was...

20:51.480 --> 20:53.560
The daughter of a distant relative.

20:53.840 --> 20:54.640
I see.

20:58.080 --> 20:58.880
Fanghao.

20:59.840 --> 21:00.880
Where are the fruits?

21:01.440 --> 21:02.440
Check on your mom.

21:12.320 --> 21:14.600
Well, she fell sick

21:14.600 --> 21:17.600
and passed away last year.

21:19.000 --> 21:20.080
I'm sorry.

21:20.400 --> 21:22.080
I didn't know.

21:22.680 --> 21:24.080
I didn't mean to bring it up.

21:24.080 --> 21:25.080
It's all right.

21:25.840 --> 21:27.720
You're getting married.

21:27.720 --> 21:29.680
Have you bought a house?

21:29.880 --> 21:31.240
Our families put together

21:31.240 --> 21:32.480
the down payment for a small unit.

21:33.280 --> 21:35.240
The house is already nicely furnished.

21:35.320 --> 21:37.480
All it needs is
a little bit of cleaning.

21:37.480 --> 21:39.640
We won't have to deal
with the formaldehyde of a new house.

21:40.040 --> 21:41.360
Great.

21:41.920 --> 21:43.720
Come, have some fruits.

21:45.080 --> 21:45.880
Knock yourselves out.

21:58.160 --> 21:58.960
Qingyu.

22:00.280 --> 22:01.080
Put this on.

22:01.560 --> 22:02.360
Thanks.

22:04.160 --> 22:06.600
Is this your secret hideout?

22:07.080 --> 22:08.400
What a view.

22:10.880 --> 22:12.720
It's nice to have a rooftop

22:12.960 --> 22:13.800
to take a rest.

22:14.360 --> 22:15.160
Well?

22:15.480 --> 22:16.800
Is the competition intense at school?

22:17.680 --> 22:20.640
Yeah. The students here
all have great grades.

22:21.280 --> 22:22.200
Don't feel stressed.

22:22.680 --> 22:24.480
It's important to have good grades,

22:25.080 --> 22:27.120
but when you become an adult,

22:27.320 --> 22:29.120
all the A's you got

22:29.120 --> 22:30.680
won't be too useful at work.

22:33.040 --> 22:34.040
What do you mean?

22:35.640 --> 22:37.920
I mean you have a long life
ahead of you.

22:38.120 --> 22:40.160
There are plenty of things
you can't learn from a textbook.

22:40.440 --> 22:41.520
Where can I learn them?

22:42.080 --> 22:43.440
Learn from your experience.

22:43.720 --> 22:46.880
The world has its way
of showing you how to grow up.

22:56.680 --> 22:57.480
You don't have to.

22:58.080 --> 22:59.640
Just take this.

23:00.160 --> 23:01.320
It's only natural to give

23:01.320 --> 23:03.160
my little sister a red envelope
after a visit.

23:03.160 --> 23:05.440
Now that you've grown up
and care about your looks,

23:05.440 --> 23:06.960
you'll have plenty of things
to spend money on.

23:07.160 --> 23:10.040
I know your mom has been
very strict with you.

23:10.360 --> 23:12.240
Consider this red envelope our secret.

23:12.240 --> 23:13.680
Don't tell your mom about it.

23:14.920 --> 23:15.600
Okay.

23:15.600 --> 23:16.720
When I get a job,

23:16.720 --> 23:18.120
I'll give one to your kid too.

23:18.920 --> 23:20.240
I should charge you an interest.

23:20.920 --> 23:22.560
It's cold out there,
so don't stay too long.

23:22.920 --> 23:24.000
I should get going.

23:25.920 --> 23:26.840
Jinrui.

23:26.840 --> 23:27.360
Hmm?

23:29.120 --> 23:31.120
Something has been bugging me.

23:31.120 --> 23:31.840
What is it?

23:34.520 --> 23:36.920
How did Beiyu die?

23:40.760 --> 23:41.560
Jinyu.

23:41.800 --> 23:42.360
Yes?

23:43.840 --> 23:46.480
Do you believe Qiao Beiyu
died of appendicitis?

23:47.320 --> 23:49.640
That's what our parents told us.

23:50.440 --> 23:52.200
She died soon after the surgery.

23:54.760 --> 23:56.560
I actually don't buy that story.

23:57.920 --> 23:59.080
Seriously? You?

23:59.880 --> 24:01.840
You believe everything Mom says.

24:01.840 --> 24:03.160
Why would you ever doubt her?

24:03.640 --> 24:05.440
Mom and Dad are always so evasive
when we bring up

24:05.440 --> 24:06.160
Qiao Beiyu.

24:06.640 --> 24:08.960
Guilt is the only explanation.

24:09.720 --> 24:11.280
What do you think the truth is?

24:12.600 --> 24:13.680
I don't know.

24:13.960 --> 24:15.480
I asked Jinrui just now.

24:16.440 --> 24:17.240
Appendicitis.

24:17.920 --> 24:19.840
Something went wrong with the surgery.

24:20.360 --> 24:22.760
A minor sickness took her life.

24:23.920 --> 24:26.760
But everyone said she died from AIDS.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.800
People believe what they want to,

24:29.920 --> 24:31.080
regardless of the truth.

24:34.840 --> 24:35.320
In fact,

24:36.600 --> 24:37.800
I am partly responsible too.

24:40.160 --> 24:42.560
I failed to guide her as a senior.

24:43.280 --> 24:44.720
That's why she went astray.

24:45.720 --> 24:46.840
She was so young.

24:47.400 --> 24:48.720
Her life had just begun.

24:49.120 --> 24:50.640
But the end came too soon.

24:52.640 --> 24:55.040
Jinrui told me the same thing
our parents did.

24:56.950 --> 25:01.830
Maybe they avoid talking about her
because they feel sad.

25:02.910 --> 25:06.030
After all, who wants
to reopen old wounds?

25:12.420 --> 25:17.670
[Huanzhou High School]

25:28.630 --> 25:29.110
What?

25:30.030 --> 25:32.270
I don't care if your dad works
at the People's Hospital.

25:32.270 --> 25:33.830
What you said was false.

25:36.990 --> 25:37.790
Qiao Qingyu.

25:38.830 --> 25:40.950
I could tell everyone
your dirty little secret.

25:41.230 --> 25:43.470
I can't control what you say,
so do whatever you want.

25:43.550 --> 25:44.910
But I won't be blackmailed again.

25:44.910 --> 25:46.950
[Despicable]

25:46.950 --> 25:47.950
I'll make you pay.

25:49.790 --> 25:50.430
Sheng.

25:52.830 --> 25:54.030
What did she write?

25:54.190 --> 25:54.950
Nothing.

25:55.790 --> 25:56.310
A love letter.

25:56.310 --> 25:56.990
Don't be silly.

25:56.990 --> 25:57.670
For real?

25:57.670 --> 25:58.270
Cut it out.

25:58.270 --> 25:58.830
Let me see it.

25:58.830 --> 25:59.670
Nothing to see here.

25:59.870 --> 26:00.710
Just a peek?

26:00.710 --> 26:01.390
It's nothing.

26:01.390 --> 26:02.190
Back off.

26:02.390 --> 26:02.990
Just one look.

26:02.990 --> 26:05.190
Sheng, let us have a look.

26:05.710 --> 26:06.030
Show me.

26:06.230 --> 26:06.950
Sheng, come on.

26:08.350 --> 26:09.430
Fine, go on.

26:11.230 --> 26:12.550
Everyone, submit your homework.

26:15.430 --> 26:17.310
Qiao Qingyu, turn in your homework.

26:39.110 --> 26:42.110
Mathematics, Chinese Language,
Physics, and Chemistry.

26:42.110 --> 26:44.030
Did you leave all your homework at home?

26:44.030 --> 26:46.430
I finished them and brought them
to school. They were here.

26:46.430 --> 26:47.630
Ye Zilin and Chen Hao

26:47.630 --> 26:49.750
said the same thing
when they didn't do their homework.

26:52.430 --> 26:53.430
I can't wait forever.

26:53.430 --> 26:54.670
I must hand in the homework.

26:56.110 --> 26:58.430
Hey, you know the drill, right?

26:58.510 --> 26:59.910
If someone doesn't finish
or bring their homework,

26:59.910 --> 27:01.550
they must rewrite it three times.

27:02.350 --> 27:03.710
None of your business.

27:04.030 --> 27:05.590
We're in different conditions.
Who knows about her?

27:44.630 --> 27:45.430
Sheng.

27:46.950 --> 27:47.950
When did you get home?

27:48.030 --> 27:49.350
You could have told me.

27:49.950 --> 27:51.030
It's nothing noteworthy.

27:51.230 --> 27:52.550
I'm leaving anyway.

27:57.350 --> 27:58.190
Stop right there!

28:02.470 --> 28:04.070
You come and go as you please.

28:04.790 --> 28:06.270
This is your home, not a hotel.

28:06.830 --> 28:08.870
My home is an old house
in Chaoyang Village.

28:09.150 --> 28:09.910
This is your home.

28:09.910 --> 28:11.030
And yours too!

28:19.350 --> 28:20.230
You barely

28:21.630 --> 28:22.950
even come home.

28:23.630 --> 28:25.390
But when you run out of money,

28:25.390 --> 28:26.430
you always show up.

28:26.550 --> 28:28.230
I want you to record

28:28.990 --> 28:30.990
every single amount I take from you.

28:31.310 --> 28:32.710
Once I've graduated from university,

28:32.710 --> 28:34.350
I'll pay you back,
including the interest.

28:34.550 --> 28:35.710
I am your father!

28:35.830 --> 28:37.310
I have a grandpa and a mother.

28:37.510 --> 28:38.310
I don't have a father.

28:39.470 --> 28:40.470
Ever since I was little,

28:41.310 --> 28:42.870
my grandpa sent me to school,

28:43.230 --> 28:44.870
picked me up, and paid the school fees.

28:45.110 --> 28:45.710
And you?

28:45.710 --> 28:46.550
You've done nothing.

28:49.190 --> 28:50.190
I was too busy.

28:50.190 --> 28:51.390
Just another excuse!

28:54.350 --> 28:55.990
My mom was right

28:55.990 --> 28:56.910
to have left you.

28:57.190 --> 28:57.990
To others,

28:57.990 --> 28:59.430
you're a lifesaving doctor.

28:59.430 --> 29:00.590
But to me,

29:00.950 --> 29:02.670
you're nothing but a selfish man.

29:02.870 --> 29:04.070
A man like you

29:04.070 --> 29:05.510
doesn't deserve to have a family.

29:05.510 --> 29:05.990
You...

30:18.870 --> 30:19.430
Hurry up.

30:19.430 --> 30:21.750
Quick.

30:23.150 --> 30:24.510
Start running!

30:24.710 --> 30:25.670
Faster!

30:28.070 --> 30:30.150
Ye Zilin, don't you dare try this again!

30:30.150 --> 30:30.950
Hurry up!

30:37.670 --> 30:38.470
Miss!

30:39.350 --> 30:40.950
Qiao Qingyu's on her period.

30:44.670 --> 30:45.470
Qingyu.

30:45.470 --> 30:46.830
Clean yourself up in the toilet.

30:52.870 --> 30:53.670
Start running!

30:59.070 --> 30:59.870
Jiang Nian.

31:00.710 --> 31:02.470
You carry an extra uniform.

31:02.470 --> 31:03.630
Could I borrow it?

31:04.070 --> 31:05.110
I can't.

31:09.910 --> 31:10.710
Qingyu.

31:12.070 --> 31:13.150
Did your sister, Qiao Beiyu,

31:13.150 --> 31:14.750
die from AIDS?

32:00.790 --> 32:01.590
What?

32:01.590 --> 32:03.030
Did you tell others?

32:03.830 --> 32:04.830
What do you mean?

32:04.830 --> 32:07.150
Did you tell everyone about Qiao Beiyu?

32:07.830 --> 32:08.870
Don't be silly.

32:08.910 --> 32:09.870
You're despicable.

32:11.030 --> 32:11.830
Qiao Qingyu.

32:12.550 --> 32:14.430
Don't attack me.

32:14.430 --> 32:15.830
You started it.

32:15.830 --> 32:17.110
That is why you are being silly.

32:17.470 --> 32:19.030
You started accusing me

32:19.030 --> 32:20.510
before you even learned anything.

32:26.190 --> 32:27.750
Borrow a uniform.

32:28.430 --> 32:29.390
Don't catch a cold.

32:38.910 --> 32:39.750
Look here.

32:40.230 --> 32:42.990
AIDS is transmitted through blood

32:42.990 --> 32:45.790
and intercourse.
A child could get it from the mother.

32:45.790 --> 32:47.590
It's not an airborne disease.

32:47.870 --> 32:48.830
Enough.

32:49.750 --> 32:50.550
Move aside.

32:51.310 --> 32:52.150
I need a nap.

32:54.870 --> 32:57.070
Look here.

33:05.150 --> 33:06.990
There was a girl called Qiao Beiyu.

33:06.990 --> 33:08.990
Her parents filed a lawsuit
against the hospital

33:08.990 --> 33:10.270
over a medical procedure.

33:10.470 --> 33:11.670
Do you remember anything?

33:13.990 --> 33:16.550
I think your father was
in charge of that.

33:16.550 --> 33:18.990
He determined
that the hospital wasn't responsible.

33:19.510 --> 33:21.070
He did as the mediation panel suggested

33:21.070 --> 33:22.230
and compensated them.

33:27.030 --> 33:29.070
I bought you the trousers just days ago.

33:29.070 --> 33:30.310
How did you ruin it already?

33:30.630 --> 33:31.750
The smudge won't come off.

33:32.310 --> 33:33.430
Your dad and I had to

33:33.910 --> 33:35.470
borrow a couple of grand

33:35.830 --> 33:36.990
so you could go to school here.

33:38.190 --> 33:39.430
Jinyu is young and insensible,

33:39.430 --> 33:40.950
but you should be more mature.

33:42.550 --> 33:43.990
My classmates were playing
during recess.

33:43.990 --> 33:45.870
They got the smudge on me.

33:45.870 --> 33:47.670
I told you to stay away from them.

33:49.070 --> 33:50.390
It was an accident.

33:50.790 --> 33:51.830
Didn't I tell you

33:52.190 --> 33:53.950
to stay away from those nasty classmates?

33:54.590 --> 33:56.070
They could be a bad influence.

33:56.070 --> 33:57.310
See? This is what you get.

33:58.390 --> 33:59.390
It's not that bad.

34:00.190 --> 34:01.230
Qiao Qingyu, listen up.

34:02.230 --> 34:04.030
You are influenced by your company.

34:04.110 --> 34:06.310
Stay with classmates who study hard.

34:06.550 --> 34:07.710
Choosing the right friends is important.

34:08.429 --> 34:09.710
Otherwise, you'll regret it

34:09.989 --> 34:11.030
when you are worse off.

34:18.190 --> 34:19.310
No one ever listens to me.

34:22.190 --> 34:23.550
It's just trousers.

34:23.590 --> 34:24.510
I'll wash them.

34:24.870 --> 34:25.670
Don't you dare!

34:29.949 --> 34:31.310
I'll get you a pair of new trousers.

34:46.110 --> 34:48.550
Why didn't you tell Mom and Dad
you were bullied?

34:48.949 --> 34:50.190
Dad never calls the shots,

34:50.350 --> 34:52.030
and you know Mom's bad temper.

34:52.710 --> 34:54.030
If she found out,

34:54.030 --> 34:55.510
things could get even worse.

34:56.070 --> 34:56.949
What do we do now?

34:57.390 --> 34:59.070
You can't keep letting them bully you.

35:00.390 --> 35:01.470
We need evidence.

35:01.550 --> 35:02.470
What evidence?

35:02.670 --> 35:05.550
The evidence that shows
Qiao Beiyu's real cause of death.

35:07.950 --> 35:10.230
Our conscience is clear.
That's all that matters.

35:10.590 --> 35:11.550
She is dead.

35:11.550 --> 35:12.980
Why bother going through the trouble?

35:12.980 --> 35:14.940
Proving Qiao Beiyu's cause of death

35:15.220 --> 35:17.220
is the only way to stop the bullying.

35:18.220 --> 35:20.580
Or else, no matter where we go,

35:20.740 --> 35:21.860
it'll be the same.

35:29.220 --> 35:30.020
Let's go.

35:49.140 --> 35:49.900
All right, everyone.

35:49.900 --> 35:51.420
Let's begin.

35:53.340 --> 35:55.540
[Appendicitis]
Turn to page 32 of the textbook.

35:55.700 --> 35:57.100
Let's have a look.

35:57.260 --> 35:59.300
Information retrieval
from online databases.

36:01.060 --> 36:03.300
As part of modern computing,
databases...

36:03.300 --> 36:06.060
[Appendicitis mortality rate]
Appendicitis is relatively safe.

36:06.620 --> 36:08.850
It rarely causes deaths.

36:08.950 --> 36:10.510
Turn on the computer

36:10.830 --> 36:12.470
and create a new form.

36:35.390 --> 36:37.390
I'm Wang Mumu from Class 1, Grade 3.

36:38.030 --> 36:40.230
I know you. They mentioned your name.

36:40.630 --> 36:42.430
I heard about you from them too.

36:42.510 --> 36:44.430
I've seen you
in the neighborhood, Qiao Qingyu.

36:45.950 --> 36:48.590
I live on Floor 8,
Block 13, Chaoyang Village.

36:48.870 --> 36:50.230
That makes us neighbors.

36:50.230 --> 36:50.630
Yup.

36:53.270 --> 36:54.230
They know each other?

36:56.110 --> 36:56.950
Why aren't you eating?

37:07.070 --> 37:08.630
Our class is cleaning the swimming pool.

37:08.630 --> 37:09.750
I have to go after this.

37:45.590 --> 37:46.430
Qiao Qingyu.

37:46.990 --> 37:49.510
You showed no signs of lying.

37:49.590 --> 37:50.750
Good acting.

37:50.830 --> 37:51.790
I didn't lie.

37:52.870 --> 37:55.230
So, are you telling me
you don't remember

37:55.230 --> 37:56.710
what you searched online

37:57.590 --> 37:58.470
in the computer class?

38:00.710 --> 38:01.790
I warned you.

38:01.830 --> 38:03.990
Don't spread lies
unless you can prove it.

38:04.030 --> 38:05.910
Even if your dad
is the hospital president,

38:05.910 --> 38:07.070
what does it prove?

38:08.790 --> 38:09.310
How about this?

38:09.710 --> 38:10.510
It's

38:10.630 --> 38:12.310
explicitly stated.

38:12.670 --> 38:13.470
Hand it over.

38:13.790 --> 38:14.590
I wouldn't.

38:14.590 --> 38:16.070
The truth might be

38:16.230 --> 38:17.150
too much for you.

38:20.030 --> 38:20.510
Hand it over!

38:23.630 --> 38:24.150
Hand it over!

38:32.670 --> 38:33.830
Qingyu fell into the water.

39:02.470 --> 39:03.510
This is not a love story.

39:03.510 --> 39:04.550
This is real action.

39:04.750 --> 39:05.590
Save her!

39:05.990 --> 39:06.910
Okay!

39:16.470 --> 39:18.110
It was a ruse, silly.

39:21.190 --> 39:22.510
That was despicable.

39:23.630 --> 39:25.310
I didn't know you'd risk your life

39:25.310 --> 39:26.630
for a document.

39:27.070 --> 39:28.430
But thankfully, I saved you.

39:28.630 --> 39:30.110
So, we are even now.

39:31.510 --> 39:32.590
Just you wait. I'll prove you wrong.

40:04.080 --> 40:07.770
♪Perhaps♪

40:08.280 --> 40:13.980
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

40:15.120 --> 40:20.520
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

40:21.520 --> 40:27.080
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

40:32.750 --> 40:36.420
♪In the future♪

40:36.880 --> 40:42.600
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

40:44.100 --> 40:49.170
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

40:50.420 --> 40:55.580
♪That never expires♪

40:59.180 --> 41:03.650
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

41:04.650 --> 41:08.320
♪Is your name♪

41:08.820 --> 41:13.920
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

41:15.000 --> 41:18.220
♪At first sight♪

41:18.650 --> 41:21.930
♪The future has been determined♪

41:22.620 --> 41:28.180
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

41:29.280 --> 41:32.820
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

41:33.280 --> 41:37.220
♪Is a place♪

41:37.520 --> 41:43.080
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

41:43.750 --> 41:47.120
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

